    "panels": [
      {
        "text": "### Triggers\n\nTriggers allow you to play sounds as your song plays.\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/229a5ebf2b63431d178dc2be090821cc-trigger-1.png",
        "key": "test-music-lab-sequences-practice-play-sequential-panel-c846fce5-8889-4bff-8a48-f717d5302c15",
        "typing": false,
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true,
        "layout": "text-bottom-center"
      },
      {
        "text": "### Triggers\n\nYou can activate triggers using buttons under the Run button.\n\nYou can also press the key on your keyboard\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/24c4e7f2c95f8426b31ae79bebefc386-trigger-2.png",
        "key": "music-lab-triggers-panel-3b7934d6-0a4f-4044-b9b8-7f75623de70f",
        "layout": "text-bottom-center",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true
      },
      {
        "text": "### Triggers\n\nWhen you press a trigger, your tracks will play \"live\" as the rest of your song plays\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/08d808fe3d529672ee81b5c58ea8e715-trigger-3.png",
        "key": "music-lab-triggers-panel-4bf95691-3ba3-40f8-b7df-64bccf9a7122",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true,
        "layout": "text-bottom-right"
      },
      {
        "text": "### Triggers\n\nYou can adjust when the sound plays to change how your song plays\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/2ab38d9a15a3f59687ee0592360d8956-trigger-5.png",
        "key": "music-lab-triggers-panel-4e2f979d-91a9-4a4e-b05f-47937578f59d",
        "fadeInOverPrevious": true,
        "layout": "text-bottom-right"
      },
      {
        "text": "Key takeaway: triggers add tracks to your song \"live\" when you press a button\n",
        "imageUrl": "https://images.code.org/aa473f1fec259dcbfa96e7b2492eef88-trigger-6.png",
        "key": "music-lab-triggers-panel-2a0be431-01b0-464e-86db-5a849c039be6",
